{
    "analysis": "We previously aggregated metric.csv over the full available series (no incident filtering) and obtained per-(cmdb_id,kpi_name) statistics (count, min/max timestamp, mean, p50, p95, max). Top groups by count (25 each) include carts, carts-db, catalogue, catalogue-db and their KPIs (cpu, mem, socket, latency-50/90, diskio, workload). The global metric table contains 1925 rows and the metric timestamps span 2024-01-20 07:05:00 UTC to 2024-01-20 07:29:00 UTC. From this we know the per-group P95 values are already available from the full-series aggregation and the metric points fall inside the incident window.",
